<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ title }} — {{ scan_date }}</title>
<style>
  :root { --bg:#0f1116; --card:#171a21; --line:#2a2f3a; --fg:#e7eaf0;
          --muted:#9aa3b2; --accent:#5b9dff; --warn:#ffb454; --good:#4ec98a; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { margin:0; background:var(--bg); color:var(--fg);
         font-family:"Segoe UI","Malgun Gothic",system-ui,sans-serif;
         line-height:1.55; }
  .wrap { max-width:1080px; margin:0 auto; padding:32px 20px 64px; }
  h1 { font-size:1.6rem; margin:0 0 4px; }
  .sub { color:var(--muted); font-size:.9rem; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .disclaimer { background:#2a210f; border:1px solid var(--warn);
                color:#ffe6bf; border-radius:10px; padding:12px 16px;
                font-size:.86rem; margin:18px 0 28px; }
  .summary { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .stat { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line);
          border-radius:10px; padding:10px 16px; min-width:120px; }
  .stat .n { font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:700; }
  .stat .l { color:var(--muted); font-size:.78rem; }
  .asof { color:var(--muted); font-size:.8rem; margin:6px 0 28px; }
  .theme { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line);
           border-radius:12px; padding:18px 20px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .theme h2 { font-size:1.1rem; margin:0 0 2px; }
  .theme .cat { display:inline-block; font-size:.72rem; color:var(--accent);
                border:1px solid var(--accent); border-radius:999px;
                padding:1px 9px; margin-right:8px; vertical-align:middle; }
  table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin-top:12px; font-size:.86rem; }
  th, td { text-align:left; padding:8px 10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
           vertical-align:top; }
  th { color:var(--muted); font-weight:600; font-size:.76rem;
       text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.03em; }
  td.num { text-align:right; font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums; white-space:nowrap; }
  .nm { font-weight:600; }
  .code { color:var(--muted); font-size:.78rem; }
  .badge { display:inline-block; font-size:.72rem; border-radius:6px;
           padding:1px 7px; background:#1f2430; border:1px solid var(--line); }
  .rel-high { color:var(--good); }
  .rel-medium { color:var(--warn); }
  .rel-low { color:var(--muted); }
  .reason { color:#cdd3de; font-size:.83rem; }
  .by { color:var(--muted); font-size:.74rem; }
  footer { color:var(--muted); font-size:.78rem; margin-top:32px;
           border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:14px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <div class="sub">스캔 기준일 {{ scan_date }} · 최근 {{ window_days }}일 · 생성 {{ generated_at }}</div>

  <div class="disclaimer">⚠️ {{ disclaimer }}</div>

  <div class="summary">
    <div class="stat"><div class="n">{{ n_themes }}</div><div class="l">테마</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="n">{{ n_stocks }}</div><div class="l">후보 종목</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="n">{{ n_dropped }}</div><div class="l">검증 탈락(미표기)</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="asof">
    기준일 — 시가총액 {{ asof_market_cap or 'N/A' }} · 재무(매출·PER) {{ asof_financials or 'N/A' }}
  </div>

  {% for t in themes %}
  <section class="theme">
    <h2><span class="cat">{{ t.category }}</span>{{ t.keyword }}</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>종목</th><th>시장</th><th>합의</th><th>관련도</th>
          <th class="num">시가총액</th><th class="num">매출 TTM</th><th class="num">PER(TTM)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for s in t.stocks %}
        <tr>
          <td>
            <span class="nm">{{ s.name }}</span> <span class="code">{{ s.code }}</span>
            <div class="reason">{{ s.relation_reason }}</div>
            <div class="by">제안: {{ s.proposed_by | join('·') }}</div>
          </td>
          <td>{{ s.market }}</td>
          <td><span class="badge">{{ s.agreement_score }}/3</span></td>
          <td class="rel-{{ s.relevance }}">{{ s.relevance | relevance_label }}</td>
          <td class="num">{{ s.market_cap_eokwon | eok }}</td>
          <td class="num">{{ s.revenue_ttm_eokwon | eok }}</td>
          <td class="num">{{ s.per_ttm | per }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>
  {% endfor %}

  <footer>
    합의(agreement) = 동일 종목을 KRX 검증 통과로 제안한 LLM 수(최대 3: Claude·GPT·Gemini).
    PER은 시가총액÷순이익 TTM(적자 종목은 N/A). 데이터 출처: KRX(FinanceDataReader)·OpenDART.<br>
    {{ disclaimer }}
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
